        (toArray): New function.
        (commandRun): Don't take first 'run' argument as the class.
        (dump): Dump arrays.
        (doPrint): Allow for three levels of printing, including none.
        (commandPrint): Ditto.
        (commandSet): Change entirely to set GJDB parameters.
        
