        (helpMsgs): Update documentation of run.
        Document new 'set' subcommands.
        (allCmds): Add 'call' command.
        (executeCommand): Ditto.
        New 'set' subcommands.
        Use new interface for commandPrint.
        
        * classes/ucb/tools/Env.java: Add printing parameters.
                
